title: BBC Last Night of the Proms 2018 [Video Album]
description:
In a World with Trump and Brexit pulling it apart, it is so refreshing to let Classical and Popular Music help put it back together again. The Sir Henry Hall concerts, better known as the Promenade Concerts run for 8 weeks every summer, sponsored by our Public Service Broadcaster and paid for by the People, it puts the Great back in Britain, just as Brexit threatens to pull our nation apart.

For just £6.00 Sterling the people can enjoy World class music and nights to remember. Join us in the Joy.

4 parts MPEG2 720P Audio is 320 at 48KHz.

Rigmar Radio - Rockin' the Free World since 1967
